Two new species of the water mite genus
Anisitsiellides Lundblad, 1941
from Australia ( Acari : Hydrachnidia: Anisitsiellidae )

The water mite genus
Anisitsiellides Lundblad, 1941
has a Gondwanan distribution, with several species known from Australia , New Zealand , Chile and Argentina (
). From Australia six species are known (
,
). All known Australian species of the genus are found in Eastern and Southeastern Australia , including Tasmania .

